<main>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="mx-auto col-11 col-sm-10 col-lg-8 col-xl-6">

        <div class="row justify-content-center">
          <h4 class="m-5">
            <strong>本当に退会しますか？</strong>
          </h4>
          <p class="text-center mb-5">
